---
const pageTitle = "Davide Santaniello | Engineering Portfolio";
---

<html lang="it">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>{pageTitle}</title>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fira+Code:wght@300;500&family=Inter:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
		<style>
			:root {
				--primary: #284b63;
				--primary-light: #3c6e71;
				--accent: #d9d9d9;
				--bg: #ffffff;
				--text: #353535;
				--glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
			}

			* { box-sizing: border-box; }

			body {
				font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
				background-color: var(--bg);
				background-image: 
					linear-gradient(rgba(40, 75, 99, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
					linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(40, 75, 99, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
				background-size: 30px 30px;
				color: var(--text);
				margin: 0;
				min-height: 100vh;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				padding: 1rem;
			}

			.hero {
				text-align: center;
				max-width: 900px;
				padding: 3rem 2rem;
				background: var(--glass);
				backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
				border: 1px solid rgba(40, 75, 99, 0.1);
				border-radius: 24px;
				box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
			}

			.badge {
				display: inline-block;
				background: var(--primary);
				color: white;
				padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
				border-radius: 50px;
				font-size: 0.8rem;
				font-weight: bold;
				letter-spacing: 1px;
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
				text-transform: uppercase;
			}

			h1 {
				font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4rem);
				font-weight: 700;
				color: var(--primary);
				margin: 0;
				line-height: 1.1;
			}

			.subtitle {
				font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				color: var(--primary-light);
				margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem 0;
			}

			.grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
				gap: 1.5rem;
				width: 100%;
				margin-top: 2rem;
			}

			.card {
				background: white;
				padding: 2rem;
				border-radius: 16px;
				border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
				text-decoration: none;
				color: inherit;
				transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				text-align: left;
			}

			.card:hover {
				transform: translateY(-8px);
				border-color: var(--primary);
				box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(40, 75, 99, 0.1);
			}

			.card h3 {
				margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
				color: var(--primary);
				font-size: 1.4rem;
			}

			.card p {
				font-size: 0.95rem;
				line-height: 1.5;
				color: #666;
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}

			.card-link {
				margin-top: auto;
				font-weight: bold;
				color: var(--primary);
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.5rem;
			}

			footer {
				margin-top: 4rem;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				color: #999;
			}

			@media (max-width: 600px) {
				.hero { padding: 2rem 1rem; }
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<section class="hero">
			<span class="badge">Studente di Ingegneria</span>
			<h1>Davide Santaniello</h1>
			<p class="subtitle">> Engineering the future, one note at a time_</p>
			
			<div class="grid">
				<a href="/notes" class="card">
					<h3>📚 Digital Garden</h3>
					<p>Il mio vault personale con appunti universitari, formule e guide tecniche, tutto in Markdown.</p>
					<span class="card-link">Esplora il Vault →</span>
				</a>

				<a href="https://github.com/davide-santaniello-eng" target="_blank" class="card">
					<h3>💻 Progetti Git</h3>
					<p>Codice, tool e sperimentazioni software. Dai uno sguardo ai miei repository pubblici su GitHub.</p>
					<span class="card-link">Vai ai progetti →</span>
				</a>

				<a href="mailto:davidesantaniello.scuola@gmail.com" class="card">
					<h3>✉️ Contatti</h3>
					<p>Se vuoi collaborare a un progetto o semplicemente scambiare due chiacchiere tecniche, scrivimi!</p>
					<span class="card-link">Manda un'email →</span>
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<footer>
			&copy; 2026 Davide Santaniello — Costruito con Astro & Quartz
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>
